Code.NativeIaC:
```bicep
resource account 'Microsoft.DocumentDB/databaseAccounts@2024-05-15' = {
  name: '<example_resource_name>'
  location: resourceGroup().location
  properties: {
    databaseAccountOfferType: 'Standard'
    backupPolicy: {
      type: 'Continuous' // Critical: enables continuous backup (PITR)
    }
    locations: [{ locationName: resourceGroup().location }]
  }
}
```

Code.Terraform:
```hcl
resource "azurerm_cosmosdb_account" "<example_resource_name>" {
  name                = "<example_resource_name>"
  location            = "<example_resource_id>"
  resource_group_name = "<example_resource_id>"
  offer_type          = "Standard"

  backup {
    type = "Continuous"  # Critical: enables continuous backup (PITR)
  }

  consistency_policy {
    consistency_level = "Session"
  }

  geo_location {
    location          = "eastus"
    failover_priority = 0
  }
}
```
